snippet.title: Umblight | Official Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Wishlist here: https://store.steampowered.com/app/3151840?utm_source=trailer

Umblight is a deckbuilder roguelite where you must combine cards to overpower your opponents. Travel through dark environments, find treasure, build your special deck filled with unique skills, and battle the creatures you meet along the way in this DND inspired adventure!

#trailer #gameplay #godot
